data.description: Beautifully appointed 2 bedroom & 2 bathroom single-family home in the highly sought-after Boca Raton Square, a No HOA community. This home sits on an expansive 9,000 square foot lot and underwent a complete rebuild in 2009. This house boasts inviting ambiance of the spacious living areas and accentuated by abundant natural light. Full impact windows and custom impact garage door, Ceramic tile flooring, Paver driveway and mature Florida landscaping. Large backyard complete with a privacy fence and oversized covered patio. Situated on one of the premier streets of the neighborhood. This A+ East Boca location is just around 2 miles from the pristine beaches of Boca Raton. Walk to the newly built Addison Mizner Elementary school, enjoy the convenience of 95, shopping, and dining options.
